Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:22.25,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.00,0:00:29.76,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't believe I just said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.33,0:00:32.53,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:35.21,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of got carried \Naway by the moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.79,0:00:38.77,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,What does Haru think?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:43.06,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.39,0:00:44.60,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Heh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.39,0:00:47.00,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:48.72,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.69,0:00:52.53,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you blushing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:00:54.58,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.58,0:00:56.18,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,He's acting mature?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.18,0:00:57.31,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.03,0:00:58.86,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.86,0:00:59.98,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.35,0:01:03.53,Tonari-main,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Go...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.18,0:01:09.54,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...  I was lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.85,0:01:12.14,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you were seriously lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:14.23,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,That's brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.64,0:01:16.59,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.88,0:01:19.35,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.92,0:01:24.14,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I feel much, much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.60,0:01:27.45,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.52,0:01:32.13,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:09.96,Tonari-ep-title-black-big,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Nuisance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:12.63,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I can't keep him at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:15.70,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,We have a pet cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.70,0:03:17.73,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that would be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:19.20,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,The cat will eat the rooster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.20,0:03:21.51,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, my cat's too scared
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:23.22,Tonari-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to come down from the dresser now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:26.04,Tonari-main,Sae,0000,0000,0000,,You brought it back, Yoshida-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:28.64,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You never stop, Saeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:32.35,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can we keep him at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:36.86,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,We had chicken coops at my grade \Nschool and middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:40.16,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,I think we had one at \Nour middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:41.13,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:43.41,Tonari-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I never noticed anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:46.13,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,So Sensei, can you ask for permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.13,0:03:47.19,Tonari-main,Sae,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:48.01,Tonari-main,Sae,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.01,0:03:50.87,Tonari-main,Sae,0000,0000,0000,,You kids have no idea how much \Nof a pain those geezers are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:53.62,Tonari-main,Sae,0000,0000,0000,,They gave permission...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:58.38,Tonari-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray!  Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:57.38,Tonari-overlap,Sae,0000,0000,0000,,What?  What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:58.38,Tonari-overlap,Sae,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:01.30,Tonari-main,Sae,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway!  You better take \Ngood care of it, Yoshida-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:03.33,Tonari-main,Sae,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Mizutani-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:07.78,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:10.80,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.  I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:12.42,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I can lend a hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:14.25,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,since it's kind of my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:18.08,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You're a nice person, Sasahara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:19.24,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me Sasayan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:20.42,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Sasayan-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:23.99,Class,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Library
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:23.99,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.31,0:04:26.54,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,That should cover everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:28.27,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,We just need to figure out what
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:29.99,handwriting 2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,1)}Kick-off Meeting\NName: Nagoya\NClothing: Feathers\NFood: Chicken feed\NShelter: Chicken coop
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:29.99,Tonari-main,,0000,0000,0000,,we're doing about the chicken coop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:32.40,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Mizutani Shizuku-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:34.79,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,please participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:35.49,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Gulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.49,0:04:37.97,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,How do you build a chicken coop?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:39.84,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I can look that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:42.29,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,You can find anything on the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:45.05,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,There's a hardware store near my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:46.98,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I could go buy the materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:51.28,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let's go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:52.93,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,We can all go over the weekend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:58.90,handwriting 3,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,The School Rooster Committee\NKick-off Meeting\NName: Nagoya\NClothing: Feathers\NFood: Chicken feed\NShelter: Chicken coop
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.82,0:04:55.52,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:57.43,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Mind if we go after my practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:58.90,Tonari-internal/narrator,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Spending the weekend with classmates...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.01,0:04:59.56,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,That's perfectly okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:00.74,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Now that that's set,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:01.92,Tonari-main,,0000,0000,0000,,it's time for the next step!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:02.49,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Next step?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.49,0:05:04.23,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Choosing a meeting place!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.23,0:05:05.65,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,You know, a location and time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:07.13,Tonari-flashbackinternal,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:08.18,Tonari-flashbackinternal,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:11.17,Tonari-flashbackinternal,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...  I was lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:14.08,Tonari-flashbackinternal,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I feel much, much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:18.55,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Should I have accepted?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:22.99,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,But that was a spur-of-the-moment \Nconfession on my part.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.79,0:05:27.84,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:33.05,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, it's clear that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.05,0:05:36.23,Tonari-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,he wasn't happy about my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:37.81,misawa,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Misawa \NBatting Center
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:37.81,Tonari-main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.97,0:05:41.50,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,You're early.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:42.96,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.45,0:05:45.15,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,We got out of practice early.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:50.07,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,W-Want to wait inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:51.08,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:58.01,Tonari-internal/narrator,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Right, I don't like being \Nalone with boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:05:59.54,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.35,0:06:06.38,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,And don't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:11.77,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:13.60,Tonari-main,,0000,0000,0000,,He was pretty handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:16.04,Tonari-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:17.77,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,'Sup, baseballer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:20.71,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Do you know him, Sasahara-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:22.84,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, I come here all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:26.81,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,What?  Are you also one \Nof Haru's friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:29.03,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:30.62,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go take a few swings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:31.40,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:35.62,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?  What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:39.18,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't lend \Nstrange people money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.18,0:06:40.04,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:41.90,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:45.67,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to hold \Nthe bat like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:47.24,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:51.64,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:53.54,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,My brother broke my alarm clock...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:55.55,Tonari-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Granny clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:07:00.31,hardwater,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hardware
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:06:59.53,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:00.49,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:01.89,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.89,0:07:03.33,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't enough money \Nin the federal budget!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.33,0:07:05.23,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Borrow money!  Take out a mortgage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:08.14,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,No!  Roosters can't find work!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:09.48,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:10.94,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave them here and \Ngo look for materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.94,0:07:11.78,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:15.49,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Gold...  Gold... Gold...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:17.62,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Brown...  Black...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:19.91,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:21.37,Tonari-main,Map,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  Aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:26.74,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:28.12,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.12,0:07:29.91,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,We need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:32.17,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Mizutani-san, how big should the...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:34.09,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Sasayan-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:36.20,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,A-Am I interrupting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:38.14,Tonari-main,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the twerp?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:41.52,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,What do you jerks think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:47.40,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Mizutani-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:48.72,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,That was scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:49.93,Tonari-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were going to fight them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:51.39,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,That's crazy talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:53.41,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been in a fight in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:55.62,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:57.80,Tonari-main,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:57.80,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, you're so slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.55,0:07:59.54,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:00.80,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:02.08,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Mizutani-san's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:09.25,Tonari-main,Tomi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:11.01,Tonari-main,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Haru!  Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:22.43,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:26.90,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:28.15,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:29.80,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Just run, Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:42.27,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You're so slow, Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:44.15,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:47.96,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but can you buy what \Nwe need, Natsume-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:50.10,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,They might still be around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:53.30,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.04,0:08:57.22,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go help her carry everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.73,0:08:59.60,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida, look after Mizutani-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:00.54,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:05.95,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:07.11,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:08.46,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:09.25,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:13.32,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,The surprises never end with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:16.23,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You sent him flying with one arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:27.20,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to say \Nto the guy I just rejected?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:29.92,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You're acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:30.82,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:33.91,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, you would refuse \Nto look after the rooster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:37.45,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You would refuse to go \Nout over the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:38.68,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,It's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:41.74,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:44.58,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,He's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:47.59,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is weirdly perceptive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:49.36,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:50.94,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:54.08,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.08,0:09:55.78,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:09:59.92,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:05.98,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,They're taking forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:10.41,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Was he worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:13.06,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.06,0:10:14.92,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,We bring goodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:22.64,misawa,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Misawa Batting Center
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:22.64,parking,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}Parking Lot
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:26.04,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Cutting wood is a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.46,0:10:29.90,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to ask the \Nstore to cut it for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:32.28,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem realistic \Nfor the four of us
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.28,0:10:34.90,Tonari-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to build this coop by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:39.36,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,I went with the simplest \Ninstructions I could find...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:42.18,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I told you we should have \Nbought that cool one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:44.02,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?  What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.02,0:10:45.69,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,You're already giving up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.69,0:10:47.02,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Sawing wood?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:48.60,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,That's grueling work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:52.28,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I have a chainsaw you can use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:54.17,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you mention that sooner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:56.21,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Man...  I'll go grab it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:10:59.30,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go buy ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:00.63,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.85,0:11:02.60,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Get me a soda flavored \NGarigari-kun popsicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:04.30,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have a Choco Monaca Jumbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:05.85,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.61,0:11:11.90,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going to finish this today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.74,0:11:16.28,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Found ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.56,0:11:18.83,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, they're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:20.57,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be too hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:24.28,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,We want to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:29.43,Tonari-main,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we kinda feel bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:34.02,Tonari-main,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,but he's been ignoring us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:35.08,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:37.33,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you apologize then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:38.92,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Mizutani-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:44.51,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's selfish to expect him to \Nlisten after you hurt his feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:46.65,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,but you're welcome to offer an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:50.03,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you don't \Ninterfere with our work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:53.16,Tonari-main,Tomi,0000,0000,0000,,This girl is cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:56.51,Tonari-main,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see that we're \Nasking you to help us out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:57.57,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Not my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:12:00.03,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.56,0:12:02.20,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,You're in love with Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:04.52,Tonari-main,Tomi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:06.09,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.09,0:12:08.04,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:09.78,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I said that I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.78,0:12:11.03,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  It's you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:12.17,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.17,0:12:14.04,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now.  Calm down, Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.22,0:12:14.04,Tonari-overlap,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:16.77,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,We're only here to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:18.50,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Mizutani-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:20.21,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:23.02,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}That hurt!  Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.02,0:12:24.99,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Get that dirty look off \Nyour face, Yamaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.99,0:12:27.05,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You're always resorting to \Nviolence like a little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.31,0:12:28.57,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,So, why are they here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:28.57,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Don't touch her like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:29.72,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.15,0:12:31.65,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.65,0:12:33.13,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.13,0:12:35.82,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,They want to make peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.39,0:12:37.44,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,As proof,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:40.44,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,they're going to help us \Nbuild the chicken coop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:42.71,Tonari-main,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,What?!  That's bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:45.10,Tonari-main,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,Why would we waste our time on that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:46.51,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to make peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:48.28,Tonari-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you need to show that you mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.21,0:12:48.28,Tonari-overlap,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Make peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:49.63,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.94,0:12:52.66,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.86,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You should have said something sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.86,0:12:57.29,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.  Come join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:12:58.75,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Too easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:01.97,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I-I've seen this happen on TV before!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:05.26,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}We're going to become \Nfriends now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:05.26,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're actually attracted to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:07.49,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,You're in love with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:07.49,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You guys aren't so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.82,0:13:09.82,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,I bought ice cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:12.68,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,I got sidetracked, so \Nit's a little melted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:14.44,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,There's more people!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:16.04,Tonari-main,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!  She's super cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:16.04,Tonari-overlap,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Next, assemble these.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:18.23,Tonari-main,Tomi,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.  She's super cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:18.23,Tonari-overlap,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:20.47,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mitty...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:21.07,Tonari-overlap,Tomi,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.47,0:13:22.57,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Who are these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:26.06,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I can build something without \Ndoing any work myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:26.78,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:27.45,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:32.45,nagoya,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Nagoya
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:32.45,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,And so, we were able to \Ncomplete the chicken coop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:34.04,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,It's not cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.26,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.26,0:13:37.49,Tonari-main,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we did a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.14,0:13:39.82,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I brought Nagoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:52.07,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,He went inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:55.24,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:56.92,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats, Mizutani-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:59.26,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't do any work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.26,0:14:00.65,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:02.86,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to touch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:04.17,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:05.90,Tonari-main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:07.49,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You ticked me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.61,0:14:14.79,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to take it \Nto school next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:15.84,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.84,0:14:18.96,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling we're \Ngoing to get yelled at.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:21.27,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Just put it in a grassy spot and it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.33,0:14:23.87,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends are a little scary,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:26.37,Tonari-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but they're nice people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:28.24,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.34,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:33.06,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?  Why did he look at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:36.35,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going this direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:37.58,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Ditto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.58,0:14:39.05,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll walk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:41.89,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,See you on Monday!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:43.09,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:44.94,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:47.33,Tonari-main,Natsu,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, why did \Nyou name him Nagoya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:48.81,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now{\i0} you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.81,0:14:50.79,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Nagoya Cochin chickens are famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:53.25,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,This is far enough, Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:54.63,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:55.16,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:14:58.30,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay with you a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:01.84,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,There he goes again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:05.16,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:10.22,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bring myself to look up at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:14.75,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:19.52,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,God decides when people get \Nto be lucky or unlucky
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:21.83,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,so everything balances out in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:24.72,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,It nets to zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.46,0:15:27.39,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't believe any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:29.81,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bunch of smoke and mirrors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.55,0:15:33.66,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I've been thinking lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:38.44,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,If meeting you was my lucky moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.99,0:15:41.32,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,it balances out everything \Nelse that's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:46.42,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Only good things have happened
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:48.56,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,since I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:55.43,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:56.57,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:15:57.93,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You win!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.61,0:15:59.89,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:07.78,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to guess \Nhow someone else feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:11.09,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I should let it all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:16.61,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You said that you felt much better
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:20.05,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,after I said that I didn't love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:23.92,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You meant what you said, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:26.41,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that you \Ndon't want my affection,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:31.01,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,but I've fallen in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.18,0:16:33.34,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.45,0:16:39.32,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty blunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:42.10,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Only because you keep playing dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.11,0:16:44.06,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:46.28,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I don't \Nwant your affection.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:49.03,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:53.20,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I've had some dirty thoughts about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:55.32,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't need to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:17:00.06,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,But my love is probably \Ndifferent from yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.82,0:17:05.33,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you would leave \Nme if you realized that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:09.13,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:20.27,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:24.34,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, let's start all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.28,0:17:28.19,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait for you to fall in love \Nwith me before I say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:34.86,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.73,0:17:42.66,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,The answer was very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.07,0:17:53.47,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we should go home, Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:17:56.09,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:01.96,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Haru said that \Nhe wants to be with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.81,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I need right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:14.49,cellphone2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(378,1)}Mi-chan\NYuzan's on his way
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:20.57,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku, don't go home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:25.08,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find a place to spend the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:29.08,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,My simple answer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:30.90,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,was immediately shot down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:32.81,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:35.80,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:39.56,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.56,0:18:42.04,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,He's so much trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:47.81,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.95,0:18:51.98,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yoshida.  Thanks for having me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.83,0:18:56.25,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:59.48,Tonari-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Shizuku-san?  This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:01.06,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't want to go home tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:03.46,Tonari-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What?!  What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.46,0:19:05.47,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Takaya, have you eaten dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:06.45,Tonari-main,Taka,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.01,0:19:07.22,Tonari-overlap,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Nice place you got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.22,0:19:09.92,Tonari-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's just a normal house...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:12.52,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't your mom around?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.52,0:19:13.83,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,She's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:16.05,Tonari-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You can stay in the guest room...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:23.68,Tonari-flashbackinternal,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find a place to spend the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:26.83,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,For a moment there, I was \Npicturing something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.28,0:19:29.99,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.78,0:19:33.02,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:35.15,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,It's just fried rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:36.94,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Did you make this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:39.40,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you watching me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:41.70,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,There's also pickled vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:43.76,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:45.99,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Like one of those countryside grandmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:53.31,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.44,0:20:06.84,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:09.22,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:13.84,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening to me, Yuzan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:32.87,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there's a spirit in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:37.20,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,H-How can you walk around \Nmy house naked like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.39,0:20:42.47,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you study at home, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:45.92,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:48.01,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't look at him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.21,0:20:51.78,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bored.  Let's play a word game.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.78,0:20:52.82,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,No, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:57.06,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, Dad always walks \Naround in his underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:20:58.90,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is this normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:02.97,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I-I guess I could sneak a peek...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.99,0:21:13.81,Tonari-main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Use the futon if you're going to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:16.76,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.76,0:21:18.38,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,He's not coming home tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.53,0:21:19.83,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:22.86,cleaners,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Sweet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.83,0:21:22.35,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,But I brought him a present!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.98,0:21:26.51,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.  Make me \Nsome tea, Mitsuyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:27.89,Tonari-main,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:40.98,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Haru's such a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:44.65,Tonari-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,He can't run away forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.06,0:21:52.76,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,He was acting a little strange,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.90,0:21:54.96,Tonari-internal/narrator,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,but maybe it was my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.10,0:23:34.80,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, why were you guys in \Nthe spray paint section?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.27,0:23:36.43,Tonari-main,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,Duh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:38.23,Tonari-main,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,For graffiti, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.64,0:23:41.39,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,It's a crime to deface public property.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.39,0:23:44.15,Tonari-main,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,It's not against the law to spray \Nthe statues in my own home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:46.44,Tonari-main,Tomi,0000,0000,0000,,His yard is full of sculptures!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.70,0:23:49.95,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Why do punks like to draw on walls?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.95,0:23:52.03,Tonari-main,Mapo,0000,0000,0000,,Because the wall's \Nasking to be drawn on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.03,0:23:54.24,Tonari-main,Tomi,0000,0000,0000,,And because walls are a \Nbig {\i1}draw{\i0} for punks!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.24,0:23:55.69,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,My point is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.69,0:23:56.45,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.77,0:23:59.52,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Yard is full of sculptures...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.91,0:24:03.46,Tonari-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,He's rich and an art buff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:05.96,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't be too...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.48,0:24:09.27,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to know why \NI named you Nagoya?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.97,0:24:10.81,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,It's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.81,0:24:11.80,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,No, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.32,0:24:14.18,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Something happened with \NNagoya Cochin in my past...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:15.46,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.46,0:24:16.46,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.97,0:24:20.98,Tonari-NextEpisode,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.97,0:24:20.98,Tonari-Next-ep-title,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Summer Break
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.52,0:24:19.66,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!  I can't tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.66,0:24:20.98,Tonari-main,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,Cut me some slack!
